- Weigh accurately 1 g of Thyroid, or proportionately less, if the iodine content is greater than 0.20 percent, in a porcelain crucible;
Weigh accurately 1 g of Thyroid, or proportionately less, if the iodine content is greater than 0.20 percent, in a porcelain crucible;
- add 7 g of Anhydrous Potassium Carbonate ;
add 7 g of Anhydrous Potassium Carbonate ;
- mix carefully, and gently tap the crucible several times to compact the mixture;
mix carefully, and gently tap the crucible several times to compact the mixture;
