overlay with 10 g more of Anhydrous Potassium Carbonate and compact the material thoroughly by tapping;
- ignite the mixture for 25 minutes at 675 to 700 C in a muffle furnace preheated to that temperature;
ignite the mixture for 25 minutes at 675 to 700 C in a muffle furnace preheated to that temperature;
- cool, add 20 mL of distilled water, or more if necessary;
cool, add 20 mL of distilled water, or more if necessary;
- heat gently to boiling, and decant through a filter into a conical flask of a suitable size;
heat gently to boiling, and decant through a filter into a conical flask of a suitable size;
